Just as https://github.com/okuchaiev/tensorflow-float16/commit/c1b6623154e14799419f91bd197b7900a78dbc2b , I modified the following three files

tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD
tensorflow/core/BUILD
tensorflow/core/kernels/BUILD

So when i execute
syj@syj-dl:~/tensorflow$ git pull --recurse-submodules

It prompts me

error: Your local changes to the following files would be overwritten by merge:
tensorflow/core/BUILD
Aborting

What should I do?
